Description: Provides elemental Statistics and Probability functions aimed 
	to teach students the main concepts of Descriptive and Inferential Statistics. 
	The main topics covered are Descriptive Statistics, Probability models 
	(discrete and continuous variables) and Statistical Inference (confidence 
	intervals and hypothesis testing).
